### 4.5 Store Manager APIs: manager.py

The manager module contains store-specific operational controls.

#### Inventory alerts

- `GET /manager/inventory/<store_id>`
- returns products in store with quantity < 10

#### Orders

- `GET /manager/orders/<store_id>`
- `POST /manager/orders/update`
  - update order status
  - optionally assign/override partner
  - mark partner availability
  - if status becomes `Delivered`, partner is freed

