  - returns full inventory with expiry, flash sale state, category

#### Flash and expiry workflows

- `POST /manager/create-expiry-combo`
  - inserts combo bundle for expiry management
- `POST /manager/dispose-restock`
  - resets store inventory quantity
  - updates product expiry date
- `POST /manager/flash-sale`
  - marks product as flash sale
  - halves price and stores original price
